LogicalColumn.name: Forecasted Participants(By Last Week Entries)
LogicalColumn.Description: This Metric Calculates the Forecasted Participants based on (Current Confirmed Participants + (Entries in Last Week * No of Weeks to Event Start date))

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: IFNULL("Core"."Fact - Event Attendance"."# Confirmed (Base Registration Count)", 0) + IFNULL("Core"."Dim - Event"."Weeks to Event", 0) * IFNULL("Core"."Fact - Event Attendance"."# of Entries Last Week - Base Registration Count)", 0)

LogicalColumn.name: Forecasted Participants(By Average for an Event)
LogicalColumn.Description: This Metric Calculates the Forecasted Participants for an event based on (Average No of Participants per day since Event Plan Start date) * (No of days between Evt Plan Start date and Event Start date)

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN IFNULL("%1", 0) = 0 OR IFNULL("%2", 0) = 0 THEN IFNULL("%3", 0) ELSE IFNULL("%3", 0) + IFNULL("%3", 0) / "%1" * IFNULL("%2", 0) END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN IFNULL("Core"."Dim - Event"."Days since Launch", 0) = 0 OR IFNULL("Core"."Dim - Event"."Days till Event", 0) = 0 THEN IFNULL("Core"."Fact - Event Attendance"."# Confirmed (Base Registration Count)", 0) ELSE IFNULL("Core"."Fact - Event Attendance"."# Confirmed (Base Registration Count)", 0) + IFNULL("Core"."Fact - Event Attendance"."# Confirmed (Base Registration Count)", 0) / "Core"."Dim - Event"."Days since Launch" * IFNULL("Core"."Dim - Event"."Days till Event", 0) END
